!*******************XDEFAULT CONFIG*****************
!*
!* Setup for all X11 apps
!* Inspiration: http://www.seas.upenn.edu/~eecad/cadence/.Xdefaults
!*
!* Use the command "xrdb < $HOME/.Xdefaults" to reread in changes to
!* .Xdefaults
